verses.roman:
ei śloka mahāprabhu paḍe bāra bāra
svarūpa vinā artha keha nā jāne ihāra

synonyms: ei śloka—this verse; mahāprabhu—Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu; paḍe—recites; bāra bāra—again and again; svarūpa vinā—except for Svarūpa Dāmodara; artha—meaning; keha—anyone; nā jāne—does not know; ihāra—of this.
translation: This verse was recited by Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu again and again. But for Svarūpa Dāmodara, no one could understand its meaning.
